## Customer Impact

- An improved drag-and-drop experience.

## Regression? 

- No

## Risk

- I haven't had to work with pointers or allocate/de-allocate memory in the last 13 years so the risk is quite high. Please do not assume that I know what I'm doing. I've studied the documentation as closely as possible and I believe I've done things correctly but there are a lot of topics covered here and I could be making some incorrect assumptions in certain cases. A real Windows programmer should take a look at this to make sure there isn't anything glaringly wrong.

